title: Covid-19 impact: J&K, others begin tracing preachers

New Delhi: Health officials in at least four states are scrambling to trace people who have been infected or are potentially at risk of being infected by the Covid-19 virus after attending a gathering of Islamic preachers in New Delhi earlier this month.
